{"tid":1584699,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方於屯門進行驅散行動","createTime":"2019-09-21T09:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T09:22:57.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c85b15125ff9e27be93e306e2d0bccc009e0715a","tid":1584699,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T09:19:22.000Z","msg":"警方於屯門進行驅散行動<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n電台及電視台當值宣布員注意：<br />\n <br />\n請盡快播出下列消息，並在適當時間重播：<br />\n <br />\n  激進示威者今日（九月二十一日）手持鐵枝，破壞屯門市中心輕鐵站設施，將雜物投入輕鐵路軌，及於附近設置路障，堵塞交通。另外，激進示威者投擲汽油彈，危害在場人士和警務人員的人身安全。<br />\n   <br />\n  警方將於短時間內採取驅散行動，並警告示威者立即停止違法行為及離開。<br />\n   <br />\n  警方提醒附近一帶市民留意情況，如有需要，盡量留在室內安全地方，並關好窗戶。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年9月21日（星期六）<br />\n香港時間17時13分<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201909/21/P2019092100666.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201909%2F21%2FP2019092100666.htm&d=ekRw3fL0jih6ME0SbOEd7%2F4XLRjZdTHGp6sdrEQ6olc%3D&h=6022779c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201909/21/P2019092100666.htm</a>"},{"pid":"125eef8d2fa3ab95d988b90a3ec21a9dab938584","tid":1584699,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T09:19:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"f8fae1170d7ab148f954be3979c5bdf47e9cc279","tid":1584699,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T09:19:58.000Z","msg":"[行動又無人理？] 全球最大親子抗爭活動上線啦！ <strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">#birdfoldingchallenge</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1584614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1584614</a><br />\n摺一隻紙鳥，影相，放上Facebook / Twitter / Instagram，並加上hashtag #birdfoldingchallenge #929